COVID-19 Cases by Race/Ethnicity:
Racial groups are defined such that: 
Asian = Asian or Pacific Islander
Black = Black or African American
Hispanic = Hispanic or Latino, regardless of race
White = White 

Rates are age adjusted according to the U.S. 2000 standard population, per 100,000 people by racial/ethnic group.
